title: Cat Harness and Lead Set, Escape-Proof Kitten Harness with Retractable Cat Lead, 5m/16.4 Ft Automatic Extendable Cat Leash for Dogs Puppy Pets Walking (blue, S)
features: 【Retractable Design】 - The dog leads features a retractable design and an ergonomic non-slip handle for an easy and secure grip. The locking button is designed with 4 modes so you can pause, lock, unlock or stretch freely. 5M retractable distance, just one touch, provides your pet with a pleasant walking experience without worrying about the leash hurting your hand

【Adjustability】- We have sturdy buckles with double D-shape buckles for cats and small dogs of different sizes. It can be adjusted according to the tightness and comfort level of your pet when wearing it. The safety insert buckle design makes it easier to use and more secure

【Reflective Design】- Durable kitten harness and lead set is made of strong nylon material and impact resistant ABS material. The reflective strap design of the carrier adds safety and visibility for dogs and their owners in the early morning or late at night

【Super Comfortable】 - The cat leash and harness set are designed to be more comfortable and stronger. The vest and leash are made of mesh fabric with soft padding to protect your cat/dog's skin. The front fabric is made of breathable and comfortable polyester, so your cat/dog won't feel stuffy

【Perfect Package】 - Package includes 1 cat leash, 1 leash and a self retractable dog leash, a set to meet all your needs. Perfect for walking, jogging, running, camping and hiking. To ensure that this carrier is more suitable for your cat or puppy. We strongly recommend that you measure your cat's neck/chest circumference before purchasing this carrier
